        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不该马上逞英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见奴才气怎消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，我道是谁，原来是他。老年兄，我想节度使乃甚等之人，他也走起金马门"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！你我坐在此间，看他怎样过去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一言未尽顷刻到"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说得有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李白、贺知章同坐。安禄山暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恼吓可恼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不生烦恼惹烦恼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒鬼无礼犯人嘲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "轻慢天子压群僚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知风色小儿曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想必是学士醉醇醪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，众位学士公，请来见礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自夸腹内文章妙"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "能屈能伸真君子"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "假陪笑险将他告"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是节度使，请见一礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔，大胆可恶，岂有此理。我想金马门，乃是先帝太祖所立，是我们翰林院学"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "士出入的道路。你是甚等之人，也敢行走。真乃无礼。我等坐在此间，看你怎"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "样过去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，学士公，这就是你的不是了。俺也曾南征北剿，挣下汗马功劳。况俺既拜"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贵妃娘娘为母，你竟敢慢待与我，真乃可恼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "节度使，我且问你，方才你说你既拜贵妃娘娘为母。她乃一朝国母，岂容你膝"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下如此无礼。你道是南征北剿，挣下汗马功劳，你有何功劳，不过是圣上宠爱"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你，老爷平素皆知。你可晓得我醉写吓蛮之事么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒也不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且听者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金马门怒恼了翰林院，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒醉辱骂安禄山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扰乱吾主心不安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时酒醉把君参。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高力士脱靴在金殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然沉醉写吓蛮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "削尔的首级挂高杆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂有此理。想我醉写吓蛮之时，杨国忠捧砚，高力士脱靴。圣上亲自御手调羹，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若非念你在朝奉君，我把你这大胆的奴才，送至君前，削尔的首级。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，节度使，学生酒醉失言，得罪了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下国夷蛮把兵变"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传旨曾将下官宣"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨国忠双手捧过砚"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也曾斗酒将诗献"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若不是番邦降表献"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！大胆可恶，我看你怎样过去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "学士公，莫怪我说，近日朝廷之事，都被你们这些文官，颠倒坏尽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，节度使，这就是你的不是了。你骂众位学士，李学士在此着恼，老夫与你"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宛转周旋，说了许多的好话，你反而说朝中之事，被我们文官坏尽。想昔日愧"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阳领兵，大战丘山，逼反贾同，围困在内，内无粮草，外无救兵。那时仰面朝"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天，叹曰：自己能有几乎为狗，何况与你，你可知作狗奉君无日乎。哎，真乃"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，年兄不必动怒，他能读了几句诗书，犹如对牛弹琴一般。待我问他几句。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，节度使，你说道朝中之事，被我文官坏尽。你有何能，你的来历，还当我"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等知晓甚么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你生来油头白粉面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肥嫩身体软如棉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谄媚邀宠不羞惭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赛过嫔妃一样般。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蛮夷无宝将你献"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然未曾对宫院"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真乃大胆。人来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（书童甲、书童乙同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲、书童乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了，老爷有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你二人，叫骂安禄山，哪个骂得入耳者，回府有赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲、书童乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赏什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每人赏酒一坛，若骂得不好，重责二十大板。只管前去叫骂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦伙计，老爷教我们叫骂节度使，你我如何敢骂呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，安禄山！"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗，大胆的狗才！你乃甚等之人，擅敢毁骂节度使，记打记责，还不与我退下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲、书童乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "节度使，请息怒，常言道得好，家主犯事，尽出门下之人，学生这厢陪罪了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫要与他一般见识。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊大胆可恶，你还不如我门下之人呢。来，"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲、书童乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只管放大胆地叫骂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲、书童乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔安禄山，我的儿吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔安禄山，我的孙子吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你骂长了一辈咧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下不为例。哎，安禄山，你且听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童乙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "安家小子真标标致，"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童乙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无耻无羞，甚么东西。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你骂得不好，待我去骂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让你去骂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，安禄山，我的舅子吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "安家小子真可耻，"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把你进贡似妾姬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与他同德一般齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童甲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弥子之下藏食子"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老年兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "学士公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是学生夸口，慢道我李白的诗书，就是我的仆人，他也知道弥子藏食子之事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老年兄这一节，你可知道否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒也不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休怪学生唐突，这篇文章，你还不曾读过呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来日领教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且附耳过来，这就是魏灵公用桃核那一桩故事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂却骂得好，只恐骂出祸来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕什么，纵然骂出祸来，他也不过进宫去，奏知贵妃娘娘，转奏天子，不用我"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在朝奉君，贬回原郡，只是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日不断我的酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你只在酒上打算，告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桃李园去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能奉陪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那里有酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么那里有酒？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是，有极好的美酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此走吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从前设宴桃李园，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒醉辱骂安禄山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺知章",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文臣岂容任轻慢，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老年兄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他无耻无羞真不堪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李白",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李白、贺知章同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，好骂吓，好骂。我如何受得了这气。哦，有了，我不免反出长安便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，李太白吓，李太白，俺不杀你，誓不为人也！正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用手捧尽湘江水，难洗今朝满面羞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安禄山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恼吓，可恼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（安禄山下。）"
        }
      ],
